FROM [Topic] AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[AuthorId] = [u].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[AuthorId], [c].[Body], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[ModifiedAt], [c].[TopicId]
    FROM [Comment] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[TopicId]
ORDER BY [t].[ModifiedAt] DESC, [t].[Id], [u].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(1) [t].[Id], [t].[AuthorId], [t].[CreatedAt], [t].[Description], [t].[ModifiedAt], [t].[State], [t].[Status], [t].[Title], [u].[Id] AS [Id0], [u].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [u].[Email], [u].[Gender], [u].[ModifiedAt] AS [ModifiedAt0], [u].[NormalizedEmail], [u].[NormalizedUserName], [u].[PasswordHash], [u].[SecurityStamp], [u].[UserName]
    FROM [Topic] AS [t]
    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u] ON [t].[AuthorId] = [u].[Id]
    WHERE [t].[Id] = @__id_0
) AS [t0]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[AuthorId], [c].[Body], [c].[CreatedAt], [c].[IsDeleted], [c].[ModifiedAt], [c].[TopicId], [u0].[Id] AS [Id0], [u0].[CreatedAt] AS [CreatedAt0], [u0].[Email], [u0].[Gender], [u0].[ModifiedAt] AS [ModifiedAt0], [u0].[NormalizedEmail], [u0].[NormalizedUserName], [u0].[PasswordHash], [u0].[SecurityStamp], [u0].[UserName]
    FROM [Comment] AS [c]
    INNER JOIN [Users] AS [u0] ON [c].[AuthorId] = [u0].[Id]
    WHERE [c].[IsDeleted] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[Id] = [t1].[TopicId]
ORDER BY [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t1].[Id]
